commit.message: Made sure that rests can't tie, 'cause I didn't think about that apparently...
Removed the Test class I accidentally forgot to take out and the debugging print statements. Made format remove any of those rude little x's.
Added a higher percentage so that eigth notes and smaller aren't within the percent error for whole notes
Made my lack of spelling consistant
Fixed some sort of mistake, idek
Fixed bugs about overflow control in Measure and Score, lets pray there are no more <3
Added format method for Score (the thing at the end which adds rests to the end of the last measure if necessary, and changes excess ties to dots)

Fixed Measure's addNote (it now checks that's there's at least a sixteenth note's worth of length left correctly, instead of checking for a whole note as it started out lol) and finished Score's addNote, hopefully it works right *crosses fingers*
updated addNote in Measure, should both add notes and update its space left
Added Note, Measure, and Score (Note is probably finished x'D)
Added basic gui and key listeners
